International COVID-19 cases and deaths, current as of Wednesday, January 6, 2021

Source: R/data.R
covnat.Rd

A dataset containing national-level ECDC data on COVID-19

covnat

Format

A tibble with 61,623 rows and 8 columns

date

date in YYYY-MM-DD format

cname

Name of country (character)

iso3

ISO3 country code (character)

cases

N reported COVID-19 cases on this date

deaths

N reported COVID-19 deaths on this date

pop

Country population in 2019

cu_cases

Cumulative N reported COVID-19 cases up to and including this date

cu_deaths

Cumulative N reported COVID-19 deaths up to and including this date

Source

http://ecdc.europa.eu/
